WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:15.000
PulseProof is a trusted second screen for fans who arrive late.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:01:19.000
The public product protects the result, runs Catch-up, saves a recap and verifies a receipt.

00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:45.000
The Judge Room runs seven fresh production checks from SSE to Solana.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:02:03.000
The reference receipt and PulseProof program are independently visible on Solana Explorer.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:24.000
Live context, spoiler-safe replay, offline retention and non-transferable proof form one complete loop.

